%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.2/vllm-orchestrator-gateway.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vLLM Orchestrator Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detector as Content Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-detector)
    participant LLM as vLLM / LLM Backend

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization header (pass-through)<br/>{"stream": false, "messages": [...]}
    Note over Gateway: Route matched → inject detector config<br/>from config.yaml route definition
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional mTLS (client cert)<br/>Forward Authorization + X-Forwarded-* headers
    Orchestrator->>Detector: Run input/output detectors<br/>(by detector name from config)
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>LLM: Chat completion request
    LLM-->>Orchestrator: LLM response
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response with detections[]
    Note over Gateway: If detections found AND<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replace response content
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original or fallback message)

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization header (pass-through)<br/>{"stream": true, "messages": [...]}
    Note over Gateway: Route matched → inject detector config
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional mTLS<br/>stream=true
    Orchestrator->>Detector: Run detectors on chunks
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results per chunk
    Orchestrator->>LLM: Streaming chat completion
    LLM-->>Orchestrator: SSE stream chunks
    loop Each SSE Chunk
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE chunk (text/event-stream)
        Note over Gateway: Parse chunk: if detections found,<br/>replace content with fallback_message<br/>set finish_reason="stop"
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE chunk<br/>(original or modified)
    end
    Gateway-->>Client: SSE: [DONE]
